\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-18831\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Pokemon &amp; Digimon yang masih super populer di seluruh dunia. Sumber gambar: playbuzz.com</p></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mungkin Yo-Kai Watch kelak bahkan bisa melewati kedua ikon ini. Siapa tahu ‘kan?</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jadi apa bro sis berminat memasuki dunia Yo-Kai Watch? Dunia dimana makhluk halus yang seharusnya seram jadi terlihat unyu dan gemesin? Maksud saya, coba saja lihat itu Jibanyan. Lucu banget lho!</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_18714\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-18714\" data-attachment-id=\"18714\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/mother-jennifer-lawrence-hadir-sebagai-kiasan-tentang-mother-earth/attachment/yokai-isi-5/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/yokai-isi-5.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Jibanya. Kucing siluman imut. Sumber gambar: amazon.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Jibanya. Kucing siluman imut. Sumber gambar: amazon.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/yokai-isi-5.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/yokai-isi-5.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-18714\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/yokai-isi-5.jpg\" alt=\"Jibanya. Kucing siluman imut. Sumber gambar: amazon.com\" width=\"60